{"tid":618210,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"貿易戰憂慮舒緩 亞洲股市反彈","createTime":"2018-04-05T15:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T00:58:00.000Z","uid":70274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d71f7451c6cfd1db27e41e9609c8cf2c034097a","tid":618210,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"法新社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（法新社東京5日電） 投資人判定近來中美 貿易戰疑慮遭到誇大後，且華爾街股市震盪走高，帶動 亞洲股市今天也從近期低點反彈。<br />\n東京股市領漲，勁揚1.5%，原因是市 場信心較趨正面，對避險日圓的需求減少，推動日圓走 貶。<br />\n<br />\n首爾股市上漲1.2%，雪梨股市上漲0.4%，而香港、 上海股市則因清明假期休市。<br />\n亞洲股市前景偏多，美股此前才經歷又一波起伏震 盪，收盤漲幅令人印象深刻。（譯者：陳乃瑜/核稿： 劉學源）"},{"pid":"1948eb04394ed133d8a676d6851302db2c135d29","tid":618210,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T23:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e9ac1324145c6371a9b84528c3623c6dd07ed3","tid":618210,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T00:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c697f868ac51c68967d9f94b2becf5b715c1e2fb","tid":618210,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T00:48:48.000Z","msg":"咁今朝呢？"},{"pid":"b44bcc198d384f1a3530047e14c631b31f7ab0a9","tid":618210,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c697f868ac51c68967d9f94b2becf5b715c1e2fb","tid":618210,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T00:48:48.000Z","msg":"咁今朝呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T00:53:11.000Z","msg":"升番啦"},{"pid":"13df0cc957966ec9eca86cb903e387c0d5a76a51","tid":618210,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-